snippet: Queen Beatrix of the Netherlands swore in the centrist government of Prime Minister Mark Rutte, who faced criticism from his party over a plan to increase health care premiums.
abstract: Queen Beatrix of the Netherlands swears in new centrist government under Prime Min Mark Rutte, even as he faces criticism from members of his own conservative party over plan to increase health care premiums.
lead_paragraph: Queen Beatrix of the Netherlands swore in the centrist government of Prime Minister Mark Rutte, who faced criticism from his party over a plan to increase health care premiums.

headline.seo: Dutch Premier, Rutte, Takes Office Amid Criticism
headline.main: Under Fire, Dutch Leader Is Sworn In
headline.print_headline: Under Fire, Dutch Leader Is Sworn In
